### 1. Registrar usuário
POST http://localhost:3001/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "teste@lotofacil.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "publicName": "Testador Primeiro"
}

### 2. Login com email/senha
POST http://localhost:3001/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "teste@lotofacil.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 3. Login com chave pública (Nostr-style) - OPICIONAL
POST http://localhost:3001/auth/login/pubkey
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "publicKey": "chave_publica_exemplo_123",
  "signature": "assinatura_hex_exemplo",
  "challenge": "auth-challenge-123"
}

### 4. Verificar token (substitua SEU_TOKEN)
GET http://localhost:3001/auth/verify
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI